cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.DB

This paper deals with the privacy implications of user mobility traces and location leaks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves data mining and analysis of large-scale mobility traces, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) or data mining (cs.DM). Additionally, the study of mobility characteristics and the implications for future policies could be classified under social and information networks (cs.SI) or social computing (cs.CY). Finally, the paper involves the management and publication of mobility data, which could be categorized under databases (cs.DB).
